\frac{a}{b+c}+\frac{b}{c+a}+\frac{c}{a+b} < 2
a=x+y
b=y+z
c=x+z
x+y+z=1
\frac{1-x}{1+x}+\frac{1-y}{1+y}+\frac{1-z}{1+z}<2
f(x)=\frac{1-x}{1+x}
\frac{1-x}{1+x}+\frac{1-y}{1+y}+\frac{1-z}{1+z}
x=y=0, z=1
x=y=0 \implies a=0
